description.en: The smash hit Curve Fever is back with a new multiplayer browser game: Curve Fever Pro. Cut off opponents, squeeze through tiny holes and unlock new powers.
description.ga_IE: Is é an Fiabhras Cuar Smash Hit Curve ar ais le cluiche nua Brabhsálaí Multiplayer: Cuar Fiabhras Pro.Gearr amach opponents, brúigh trí phoill bheaga agus díghlasáil cumhachtaí nua.
